Uttar Hindusthani padhatiche ani Khajuraho mandirachya todis tod aslele Markanda he devasthan vidarbhat Gadchiroli zillyatil Chamorshi talukyat ahe.
Bernardchya taryanantar yachi yogya gati sarvat jasta aahe.
imartinchya navakarita Marathitil 'Sundar-Aakarshak' navache ek pustak ya Vidyapithane tayar kele ahe.
ha vimantal Dakshin Afriketil dusrya tar Afriketil teesrya kramankacha sarvadhik vardalicha vimantal ahe.
Tarunaisathi Kardalivan parikrama mhanje ek sahasi aadhyatmik tracking ani paryatan aahe.
Ishtalinga diksha sanskar

buddhichya uprokta kshamata vikasit karun antarik adhyayan prakriya nirdosh karnyasathi darshanik tatwache aalodan karun sanshodhikene ek mahina samayawadhicha abhyaskram tayar kela jo shravan, pramanyukta manan, anuvad yane yukta hota.
